entries.femaleVariant: Somethin'...? Out with it, don't be shy!
Egh, not so kindly. I mean, there's no shortage of customers, but... someone's always harassin' me. Y'know, Jesus-freaks or people from the mayor's office. "Offends public decency."
Crazy, right? You can sell guns on every corner and nobody bats an eyelid. But put up a stall with vibrators and all hell breaks loose! Ugh!
